WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:08.258
<i>Earth.</i>

2
00:00:08.258 --> 00:00:11.386
<i>A cradle for
unimaginable beauty</i>

3
00:00:11.386 --> 00:00:14.764
<i>and staggering wonder.</i>

4
00:00:14.764 --> 00:00:18.476
<i>Incomprehensible.
overwhelming.</i>

5
00:00:18.476 --> 00:00:23.732
<i>this planet mocks our
feeble power to describe it.</i>

6
00:00:23.732 --> 00:00:28.778
<i>Yes. to truly appreciate
the astounding grandeur</i>

7
00:00:28.778 --> 00:00:34.159
<i>of this planet. sometimes
you must defile it.</i>

8
00:00:34.159 --> 00:00:37.537
<i>Behold the defiler.</i>

9
00:00:37.537 --> 00:00:43.460
<i>His character is vile.
base. and depraved.</i>

10
00:00:43.460 --> 00:00:45.837
<i>Once a proud talk show host.</i>

11
00:00:45.837 --> 00:00:49.507
<i>he has been driven by
a changing ecosystem</i>

12
00:00:49.507 --> 00:00:52.844
<i>to a drier and
harsher climate--</i>

13
00:00:52.844 --> 00:00:55.638
<i>the weekly podcast.</i>

14
00:00:55.638 --> 00:01:01.144
<i>Here. without the nourishment
of his studio audience.</i>

15
00:01:01.144 --> 00:01:05.440
<i>this clown with
dull. tiny eyes.</i>

16
00:01:05.440 --> 00:01:08.318
<i>the eyes of a
crudely painted doll.</i>

17
00:01:08.318 --> 00:01:12.614
<i>is forced to feed on that
meagerest of morsels.</i>

18
00:01:12.614 --> 00:01:15.700
<i>the random call-in fan.</i>

19
00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.830
<i>Unhinged by the feral scent
of their mild enthusiasm.</i>

20
00:01:20.830 --> 00:01:25.543
<i>he scavenges in distant
lands uninvited.</i>

21
00:01:25.543 --> 00:01:29.297
<i>fueled by a bottomless
hunger for recognition</i>

22
00:01:29.297 --> 00:01:31.675
<i>and the occasional selfie.</i>

23
00:01:31.675 --> 00:01:34.761
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

24
00:01:34.761 --> 00:01:39.683
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25
00:01:39.683 --> 00:01:42.477
<i>This is madness.</i>

26
00:01:42.477 --> 00:01:44.688
<i>This is lunacy.</i>

27
00:01:44.688 --> 00:01:46.606
<i>This is chaos.</i>

28
00:01:50.235 --> 00:01:53.780
<i>This is "Conan
O'Brien Must Go."</i>

29
00:01:56.408 --> 00:01:58.576
<i>Thailand.</i>

30
00:01:58.576 --> 00:01:59.577
<i>Hey. Conan.</i>

31
00:01:59.577 --> 00:02:01.371
I'm Anna. and I'm
calling from Thailand.

32
00:02:01.371 --> 00:02:02.539
So tell us a little
bit about yourself.

33
00:02:02.539 --> 00:02:03.540
Where do you live?

34
00:02:03.540 --> 00:02:06.209
I live in Bangkok.
the capital city.

35
00:02:06.209 --> 00:02:08.753
And right now I'm
living with my mom.

36
00:02:08.753 --> 00:02:10.338
How's that going?

37
00:02:10.338 --> 00:02:13.216
It can be quite
hard when. you know.

38
00:02:13.216 --> 00:02:15.969
I'm working from home
and I have to be on Zoom.

39
00:02:15.969 --> 00:02:19.055
and my mom will
always yell outside.

40
00:02:19.055 --> 00:02:20.598
What kind of things
does she yell at you?

41
00:02:20.598 --> 00:02:23.560
Anna! Do you want dinner?

42
00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:27.022
If I could talk to her.
maybe I could explain to her

43
00:02:27.022 --> 00:02:29.441
that it's very important
that Anna do her work.

44
00:02:29.441 --> 00:02:31.860
and you've got to stop yelling.

45
00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:34.112
Why do you think she
would listen to you?

46
00:02:34.112 --> 00:02:37.490
<i>[lively traditional music]</i>

47
00:02:37.490 --> 00:02:43.121
<i>♪ ♪</i>

48
00:02:48.835 --> 00:02:49.961
Hey.

49
00:02:49.961 --> 00:02:51.713
Hi!

50
00:02:51.713 --> 00:02:53.882
Wait. Hold on. Okay.
- Yeah.

51
00:02:53.882 --> 00:02:55.717
Okay. I can come in?

52
00:02:55.717 --> 00:02:57.385
Yes. you can. but you need to
take your shoes off. though.

53
00:02:57.385 --> 00:02:59.220
Take my shoes off?
Yes. of course.

54
00:02:59.220 --> 00:03:00.805
I respect that.
- Oh.

55
00:03:00.805 --> 00:03:01.890
Okay. Wow.

56
00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:03.975
You seem somewhat-- you
seem a little. like--

57
00:03:03.975 --> 00:03:06.603
I'm so shocked
that you're here.

58
00:03:06.603 --> 00:03:07.937
- Thank you for--
- Yeah.

59
00:03:07.937 --> 00:03:09.356
Well. you didn't really
invite me. I don't think.

60
00:03:09.356 --> 00:03:10.482
but I'm here anyway.

61
00:03:10.482 --> 00:03:12.317
[speaking Thai]

62
00:03:13.860 --> 00:03:15.445
- Hi.
- Hi.

63
00:03:15.445 --> 00:03:17.572
[speaking Thai]
- [speaking Thai]

64
00:03:17.572 --> 00:03:18.948
[speaking Thai]

65
00:03:18.948 --> 00:03:20.658
I am Conan.

66
00:03:20.658 --> 00:03:22.327
Is she a big fan of mine?
- Hmm?

67
00:03:22.327 --> 00:03:23.578
Not a big fan.

68
00:03:23.578 --> 00:03:26.581
Have you seen me on
TV. you know. ha. ha?

69
00:03:26.581 --> 00:03:28.750
Oh. very good.
I like. [laughs]

70
00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:30.418
- She doesn't know you.
- She's lying.

71
00:03:30.418 --> 00:03:31.419
She has no idea.

72
00:03:31.419 --> 00:03:32.962
Why is she lying then?

73
00:03:32.962 --> 00:03:34.172
[laughs]

74
00:03:34.172 --> 00:03:36.216
You realize I'm a
celebrity in America?

75
00:03:36.216 --> 00:03:38.760
Not at the top. no.
kind of in the middle.

76
00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:40.428
Just take my word for it.

77
00:03:40.428 --> 00:03:43.431
Like. I wouldn't get invited
to a--like. an Oscar party.

78
00:03:43.431 --> 00:03:45.392
But if there was an Emmy
party. they would think--

79
00:03:45.392 --> 00:03:47.352
what are you doing?
What is she doing?

80
00:03:47.352 --> 00:03:48.770
What is she doing?
- I don't know.

81
00:03:48.770 --> 00:03:50.522
Why are you doing
these weird things?

82
00:03:50.522 --> 00:03:52.023
What's happening right
now? I don't know.

83
00:03:52.023 --> 00:03:53.983
She's frightening me.
Can I call you Mom?

84
00:03:53.983 --> 00:03:55.944
- Yeah. Okay. Okay.
- Okay.

85
00:03:55.944 --> 00:03:57.445
Mom. I'm friends with Anna.

86
00:03:57.445 --> 00:03:59.030
- Mm-hmm.
- Yeah.

87
00:03:59.030 --> 00:04:01.199
And we have a problem
that I wanna help fix

88
00:04:01.199 --> 00:04:03.535
with your daughter.
- No.

89
00:04:03.535 --> 00:04:05.662
Yes. well. we--
we do. actually.

90
00:04:05.662 --> 00:04:06.913
[laughs]

91
00:04:06.913 --> 00:04:09.207
Okay. you're laughing.
but I'm being honest.

92
00:04:09.207 --> 00:04:10.875
She works in the house.

93
00:04:10.875 --> 00:04:13.044
Mm-hmm. She works. She
works in the house.

94
00:04:13.044 --> 00:04:14.462
I mean no disrespect.

95
00:04:14.462 --> 00:04:16.798
Mm-hmm. No problem.

96
00:04:16.798 --> 00:04:21.678
You are loud sometimes
when she's trying to work.

97
00:04:21.678 --> 00:04:23.054
Let's work on a new way.

98
00:04:23.054 --> 00:04:25.390
So this is where I talk
to you on the podcast.

99
00:04:25.390 --> 00:04:26.391
Yes.

100
00:04:26.391 --> 00:04:27.726
So you're clicking
away on your work.

101
00:04:27.726 --> 00:04:29.394
- Yep.
- Anna!

102
00:04:29.394 --> 00:04:30.979
- Oh. my God.
- Anna!

103
00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:34.733
Anna!
- Okay. okay.

104
00:04:34.733 --> 00:04:37.527
Come on in. Mom. Come in. Hi.

105
00:04:37.527 --> 00:04:39.863
Okay. okay. No. no.

106
00:04:39.863 --> 00:04:40.905
Here. here.

107
00:04:40.905 --> 00:04:43.158
Too--too loud. too loud.

108
00:04:43.158 --> 00:04:44.576
Too loud.

109
00:04:44.576 --> 00:04:45.702
Try it this one.

110
00:04:45.702 --> 00:04:46.828
[softly] Anna.

111
00:04:46.828 --> 00:04:47.912
Try now.

112
00:04:50.248 --> 00:04:52.125
[softly] Anna.

113
00:04:52.125 --> 00:04:54.544
- Anna.
- Okay. again.

114
00:04:54.544 --> 00:04:59.424
Anna. Anna. Anna. Anna.
Anna. not listen to me.

115
00:04:59.424 --> 00:05:01.009
but you stay here.

116
00:05:01.009 --> 00:05:04.888
You listen to me. Why?
- [laughing]

117
00:05:04.888 --> 00:05:06.556
Ah! Ah!

118
00:05:06.556 --> 00:05:08.099
She attacked me!

119
00:05:08.099 --> 00:05:10.101
Do you think your mother
is listening to me?

120
00:05:10.101 --> 00:05:11.603
Is she gonna change?

121
00:05:11.603 --> 00:05:14.689
[both speaking Thai]

122
00:05:15.774 --> 00:05:17.817
- I'm promise.
- You promise?

123
00:05:17.817 --> 00:05:18.818
I promise.

124
00:05:18.818 --> 00:05:20.070
You are such an actress.

125
00:05:20.070 --> 00:05:21.613
I don't believe
her for a second.

126
00:05:21.613 --> 00:05:23.073
Okay. okay.

127
00:05:23.073 --> 00:05:25.241
[laughs]

128
00:05:25.241 --> 00:05:27.118
What's with all the
exercise equipment?

129
00:05:27.118 --> 00:05:29.204
Oh. yeah.
- It's good.

130
00:05:29.204 --> 00:05:30.288
What are you doing to my ears?

131
00:05:30.288 --> 00:05:31.790
What are you doing?

132
00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:32.874
- [groans]
- Ow!

133
00:05:32.874 --> 00:05:34.376
- Whoa!
- Ow!

134
00:05:34.376 --> 00:05:35.794
- [grunts]
- God!

135
00:05:35.794 --> 00:05:37.212
Not--ow.

136
00:05:37.212 --> 00:05:39.881
Anna! Anna!

137
00:05:39.881 --> 00:05:41.633
- Not stay here.
- [groans]

138
00:05:41.633 --> 00:05:44.135
- Not stay here.
- Ow!

139
00:05:44.135 --> 00:05:45.887
Oh. Ow.

140
00:05:45.887 --> 00:05:47.597
Ow. Ow!

141
00:05:47.597 --> 00:05:48.682
You hit me.

142
00:05:48.682 --> 00:05:51.017
No. that one is
exercise for you.

143
00:05:51.017 --> 00:05:52.894
That's not exercise for me.

144
00:05:55.146 --> 00:05:56.314
Incredible.

145
00:05:56.314 --> 00:05:59.109
It's--[laughing]
- Not good?

146
00:05:59.109 --> 00:06:01.903
- I like you very much.
- I like you.

147
00:06:01.903 --> 00:06:03.488
If you ever need
help with anything.

148
00:06:03.488 --> 00:06:05.990
just yell my name--Conan.

149
00:06:05.990 --> 00:06:13.039
[screaming] Conan!

150
00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:15.333
<i>Only a fool would end their
first long day in Bangkok</i>

151
00:06:15.333 --> 00:06:18.753
<i>after a 20 hour flight
by agreeing to sing</i>

152
00:06:18.753 --> 00:06:22.007
<i>on a hit TV show in
a foreign language.</i>

153
00:06:22.007 --> 00:06:24.009
<i>I was that fool.</i>

154
00:06:24.009 --> 00:06:25.760
How are you? Nice to see you.
- Nice to see you.

155
00:06:25.760 --> 00:06:27.637
I am jet lagged.

156
00:06:27.637 --> 00:06:30.432
I'm a little out of it.
and I don't speak Thai.

157
00:06:30.432 --> 00:06:32.308
But I think I can do this.

158
00:06:32.308 --> 00:06:34.144
I'm a real song and dance man.

159
00:06:34.144 --> 00:06:35.812
whatever you guys--
where are you?

160
00:06:35.812 --> 00:06:38.440
Whatever you guys need.
I can do it. okay?

161
00:06:38.440 --> 00:06:42.277
I'm agile. I'm still
spry for my age.

162
00:06:42.277 --> 00:06:43.653
Oh. sorry.

163
00:06:43.653 --> 00:06:47.198
That person just saw
an old red-headed woman

164
00:06:47.198 --> 00:06:49.492
doing leg squats and ran away.

165
00:06:49.492 --> 00:06:51.244
Tell me if there's
anything you need.

166
00:06:51.244 --> 00:06:52.495
Yes.

167
00:06:52.495 --> 00:06:56.249
I need to be able
to speak Thai.

168
00:06:56.249 --> 00:06:58.793
and I need to be able
to sing this song.

169
00:06:58.793 --> 00:07:00.670
And I need more
talent than I have.

170
00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:02.505
Those are the three
things I need.

171
00:07:02.505 --> 00:07:04.549
- In 30 minutes?
- 30 minutes.

172
00:07:04.549 --> 00:07:06.551
This is Jen. who's
helping us out.

173
00:07:06.551 --> 00:07:08.470
Here.

174
00:07:08.470 --> 00:07:11.848
[singing along in Thai]

175
00:07:11.848 --> 00:07:13.058
What's the song about?

176
00:07:13.058 --> 00:07:15.477
It's. like. about
someone in the corner

177
00:07:15.477 --> 00:07:19.105
that. like. he's looking
at and having a crush on.

178
00:07:19.105 --> 00:07:20.315
Oh. it's. like. a
song about a creep.

179
00:07:20.315 --> 00:07:22.650
Yeah. Possibly a stalker.

180
00:07:22.650 --> 00:07:24.194
Here. you be the--
you're the girl. right.

181
00:07:24.194 --> 00:07:25.362
and you're here just
minding your own business.

182
00:07:25.362 --> 00:07:26.738
- Uh-huh.
- And then--

183
00:07:26.738 --> 00:07:30.909
Yeah. exactly. Not
that scary. [laughs]

184
00:07:30.909 --> 00:07:32.911
[clears throat] Here we go.

185
00:07:32.911 --> 00:07:35.997
[singing along in Thai]

186
00:07:38.291 --> 00:07:41.086
Mai plot pai--is that "phai"?

187
00:07:41.086 --> 00:07:42.420
<i>Mai plot phai.</i>

188
00:07:42.420 --> 00:07:43.588
What does that mean.
"mai plot phai"?

189
00:07:43.588 --> 00:07:44.964
- Not safe.
- Not safe?

190
00:07:44.964 --> 00:07:46.007
Yes.

191
00:07:46.007 --> 00:07:47.592
It's a song about a creepy guy

192
00:07:47.592 --> 00:07:49.219
who's making the
woman feel not safe.

193
00:07:49.219 --> 00:07:51.596
What a wonderful ballad.

194
00:07:51.596 --> 00:07:54.599
[singing along in Thai]

195
00:07:54.599 --> 00:07:57.602
<i>[soft pop music playing]</i>

196
00:07:57.602 --> 00:08:04.693
<i>♪ ♪</i>

197
00:08:05.944 --> 00:08:07.320
Time to go. Time to go.

198
