Thank you.

205
00:08:36.808 --> 00:08:38.101
Thank you. Thank you very much.

206
00:08:38.101 --> 00:08:39.477
Welcome to "The Wall Song."

207
00:08:39.477 --> 00:08:42.939
This is a huge treat for me.

208
00:08:42.939 --> 00:08:44.274
Yes!

209
00:08:44.274 --> 00:08:47.610
[speaking Thai]

210
00:08:47.610 --> 00:08:49.487
[laughter]

211
00:08:49.487 --> 00:08:51.573
I got off a plane
four hours ago.

212
00:08:51.573 --> 00:08:53.241
I don't know what's happening.

213
00:08:53.241 --> 00:08:54.951
[laughter]

214
00:08:54.951 --> 00:08:58.455
[speaking Thai]

215
00:09:02.334 --> 00:09:04.127
And do you know that you
come to this program.

216
00:09:04.127 --> 00:09:07.797
