217
00:09:07.797 --> 00:09:10.633
I'm jet-lagged and I
don't know the language.

218
00:09:10.633 --> 00:09:12.218
Let's give it a
shot. Gentlemen.

219
00:09:12.218 --> 00:09:13.511
Okay.

220
00:09:13.511 --> 00:09:15.055
