226
00:09:48.797 --> 00:09:52.384
<i>[zany cartoon sound
effects playing]</i>

227
00:09:52.384 --> 00:09:58.890
<i>♪ ♪</i>

228
00:09:58.890 --> 00:10:01.059
[laughter]

229
00:10:01.059 --> 00:10:04.437
I--I don't know where I
am or what is happening.

230
00:10:04.437 --> 00:10:05.939
But God bless you all.

231
00:10:05.939 --> 00:10:07.982
And really. what you're
doing here is God's work.

232
00:10:07.982 --> 00:10:09.317
I really believe that.

233
00:10:09.317 --> 00:10:10.902
and I'm gonna go to
the nearest hospital.

234
00:10:10.902 --> 00:10:12.404
Thank you very much.
- Thank you.

235
00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:17.701
<i>After my appearance.
I needed protection</i>

236
00:10:17.701 --> 00:10:20.078
<i>from angry Thai viewers.</i>

237
00:10:20.078 --> 00:10:21.246
Meet Pon.

238
00:10:21.246 --> 00:10:23.832
Pon is my security guard. yes?
- Yep.

239
00:10:23.832 --> 00:10:28.128
'Cause there's this notion
someone had that people here

240
00:10:28.128 --> 00:10:30.338
in Thailand would
just go so crazy

241
00:10:30.338 --> 00:10:33.883
