to attack me so far?

243
00:10:36.094 --> 00:10:37.178
No.

244
00:10:37.178 --> 00:10:38.596
Does anyone seem that excited?

245
00:10:38.596 --> 00:10:39.597
No.

246
00:10:39.597 --> 00:10:41.516
I'm gonna come at you
in a few different ways.

247
00:10:41.516 --> 00:10:42.517
and you show me
what you would do.

248
00:10:42.517 --> 00:10:43.685
I'll do it in slow motion.

249
00:10:43.685 --> 00:10:45.687
I'll kill you. Pon.

250
00:10:47.939 --> 00:10:49.107
I'll get you. Pon.

251
00:10:49.107 --> 00:10:51.609
[laughter]

252
00:10:51.609 --> 00:10:53.445
I'll get you. Pond.
- [grunting]

253
00:10:53.445 --> 00:10:55.572
Oh!

254
00:10:55.572 --> 00:10:56.865
I'm very impressed.

255
00:10:56.865 --> 00:10:59.451
